note.content:
-Added Classes Record -Updated Action to update user types from basic/sys admin -Added Action to add new users to an existing class
-Added ability to create more than one group in the environment
-Added validation to the editable grid for adding users so that you cannot add a user who already exists.
-Added required field to set the supervisor and add real email if needed and update user profile accordingly to the initial tasks.
-Changed name back to CLASS
-Removed constant for group and IS BASIC USER, as it depends on how many groups and which groups are being acted upon.
By Jenny 2016-09-28
